---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="AJ Gamble | Strategic Operations & Sales"
	description="Driving operational excellence and revenue growth."
	heroImage="/Gemini_copy_Generated_Image_2r54f22r54f22r54.jpg"
>
<div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem 0;">
        <a href="/about" style="background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight:  bold; border-radius: 4px;">
            View My Operational Philosophy
        </a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h2>The Strategic Edge</h2>
        <p>I don't believe in "band-aid" fixes. I believe in architectural solutions that eliminate bottlenecks, optimize throughput, and maximize customer value.</p>
    </div>
    <section style="margin: 4rem 0; padding: 3rem; background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Operational Impact</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center;">
            <div>
                <p style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">55% &rarr; 95%</p>
                <p style="color: #555;">On-time delivery performance turned around at McKissick Products</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$31M &rarr; $82M</p>
                <p style="color: #555;">Annual revenue scaled in 4 years at The Crosby Group</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$1.2M</p>
                <p style="color: #555;">Annual sales at Industrial Splicing, outperforming the next agent by 30%+</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem; text-align: center;">
            <a href="/experience" style="color: #000; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">
                See the full case studies &rarr;
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
